reviewText: What did I do? Seemed like a good idea, 3 guys kidnap 3 guys who did them wrong. 100 bucks to make it, sound is crappy, the camera is jumpy. this was 12 minutes and the end of it????? it just ends no explanation....just ends. I think I paid 15 dollars for 12 minutes of garbage and no ending or explanation of the ending...art film, don't think so. But it did seem like a good idea.
